{"tid":2491373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係happy Friday 但我好想發男朋友脾氣","createTime":"2021-04-16T09:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T10:23:08.000Z","uid":270457,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbb0bb36a2826045f731a1d2126caca02bd1bbd","tid":2491373,"uid":270457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"diu呀 越諗越嬲<br />\n港島過九龍好遠咩？<br />\n我次次從新界過港島南區搵你都係咁啦！<br />\n拍拖前就講［我可以過黎接你收工架(klb)]結果<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">一齊到而家３個月一次都無呀！</span></span>（除咗有次星期６咁岩過黎九龍）<br />\n次次都係我黎搵你就有得見 明明你一直都係WFH咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次見完我又要從港島南區搭巴士返屋企<br />\n我明港島人係覺得去九龍新界遠過去台灣，但係次次都要個女朋友從新界去港島搵你， weekend個活動範圍都係港島， 想話去踩下單車都就唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今個星期收工我都無過港島搵你，你好嘢呀 你都唔會講出黎見下食個飯咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似1-4唔見都好正常咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗過架啦，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我今晚就算約人係中環食飯我都唔會黎搵你架！你打機打飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"pink\">其實你係唔係唔鐘意我姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>